</li>
<li>
<p>Bernardo, A.B., Esteban, M., Fernández, E., Cervero, A., Tuero, E., &amp; Solano, P.A. (2016). Comparison of Personal, Social and Academic Variables Related to University Drop-out and Persistence. Frontiers in Psychology, 7.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Ortiz-Lozano, J.M., Rua-Vieites, A., Bilbao-Calabuig, P., &amp; Casadesús-Fa, M. (2018). University student retention: Best time and data to identify undergraduate students at risk of dropout. Innovations in Education and Teaching International, 57, 74 - 85.</p>
</li>
<li>
